name: Visa Från Utanmyra
comments: This is the sound of Scandinavia. Whenever i travel outside i take it with me...so that i can listen to it when i get homesick.
Hear also Jussi Björling - Nämner du Sverige (on spotfy as Nammer du Sverige" (Sic!).
Those blue tones sends shivers down my spine...
When I was younger I always thought this was the most boring song in the world. Now I love it!
I wrote this song at the age of 7.
Jan Johansson was a great artist! This is traditional swedish folkmusic and I love it!
I dont agree with the use of the f-bomb when describing this song, but it might just be the greatest song ever. Well together with "Sverige".
this is the fucking best song in the world. i love love love it so very very much!!!
